mr                                    macro                                   mr

NAME
     mmrr - move to a given angle of specular reflection

SYNOPSIS

     mmrr aallpphhaa

DESCRIPTION

     The mmrr macro is used to move to a given angle aallpphhaa of specular reflection
     (AALLPPHHAA==BBEETTAA).  In contrast to the macro mmaabb, mmrr moves the detector into the
     plane of incidence.

EXAMPLE

     mmrr 1100mmrr

